Energy Ventures Inc said it formed anew subsidiary, EVI Inc, that will seek to fund growth of andoffer financial services to oil service and equipmentcompanies.    The new unit is majority owned by Energy Ventures. Simmonsand Co Finance, an affiliate of Houston-based Simmons and CoInternational, is minority shareholder.    Initial capital of 25 mln dlrs was provided by EnergyVentures with an additional one mln dlrs contributed by Simmons. Reuter&#3;